msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Please take one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Oh, here y'go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Hm? What is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "A free stationery sample!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "We use quality paper to give weight\r\nto your heartfelt feelings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Write a thank you note to someone\r\nyou might owe! How about it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "A thank you letter, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "If you like our products, please buy\r\nmore at the stationery store!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Please take one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Hm? No one's here...\r\nDid Mama go out on an errand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "These smalltown bars... Geez."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Gets me thinking though... I've hardly\r\nbeen here long, yet they feel like family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Drinking and laughing with them,\r\nhearing out their troubles..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "I haven't had that in a really long time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "I owe these people my gratitude\r\nfor giving me a place like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Wait, gratitude...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "That reminds me, I have this stationery set. \r\nThey said I should express heartfelt feelings..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Hrm... I'm not much of a writer..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "But I guess I can try.\r\nThe mama here deserves a letter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Greetings..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "I'm sure this letter comes as a bit of a surprise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "I figured some things can't be conveyed \r\nin spoken words, so I picked up a pen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "I've had a great time ever since\r\nI dropped in here for the first time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "You accepted even an outsider like me with\r\ndrinks and songs, and that makes it special."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "I find myself staying longer and longer..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "And I'm sure the reason this bar feels so\r\nwarm is because you've made it that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I remember the first time I shared\r\na drink with you pretty clearly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "And whenever I've felt down,\r\ndrinking here cheered me right up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "You've made me realize just how important\r\nit is to have a companion you can count on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Thank you.\r\nBe who you are and don't ever change."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "If you're interested, I'd like to treat you \r\nto a meal. I'll be waiting at the ferry dock."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "All the best."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "There... Good to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Now, how do I give her the letter?\r\nI can't just hand it to her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "It'd be better if I hid it somewhere in\r\nthe bar only Mama could find."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "She'll probably clean up a bit when she\r\ngets back, so she'll find it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Okay, let's find a hiding spot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "I haven't hidden the letter yet.\r\nI've got to hide it before I go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "The new karaoke machine. I'm sure Mama \r\nwould find it pretty easily when she cleans it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Should I hide the letter here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll put it here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Nah, I'll look around more."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "The darts machine is what catches the eye.\r\nThis would be a good hiding spot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "This is the table we all use...\r\nIt'll be easy to notice if I put it here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Should I hide the letter here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "I'm sure anyone could find it\r\nif I left it on the counter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "A baseball poster... It draws the eye to it.\r\nI'll just slip it in behind the poster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "The electric pot...\r\nThe guys never seem to use it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Well... I told her to meet me at the ferry\r\ndock, but I've got some time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "I'll kill some time wandering around a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Mama hasn't read the letter yet. I should wait\r\na bit more before going to the ferry dock."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Oh, it's about time I meet up with Mama.\r\nI should go to the ferry dock."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Sorry, did I make you wait?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Nah, I just got here myself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "What!? G-Gen-san...!\r\nWhy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Buddy, y'surprised me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "The bar was empty, so I went to do some\r\nkaraoke. That's when I saw your letter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Oh no... Of course Gen-san would find it\r\nbefore Mama in the karaoke machine..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Your letter made me happy, Kiryu-san...\r\nI had no idea y'thought the world of me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Well, you taught me a lot about technology.\r\nSo I wanted to show my gratitude somehow..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "I ain't so sure I can live up to your\r\nimpression of me, but... I'll try my best!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I should probably put a stop to this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Yeah, so, that's why I'm grateful!\r\nSee you at the bar!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Huh, hey, Kiryu-san!? I didn't get to\r\ntalk... No need t'be so shy, man..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "No... I just got here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "What!? A-Ando-san...!\r\nWhy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "What do you mean, \"why?\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "The bar was empty, so I went t'play\r\nsome darts and I found yer letter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Oh no... I should have known Ando might\r\nfind it by the darts instead of Mama..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "But I had no idea that y'thought\r\nso highly of me, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Well, you sell me lots of things, so I\r\nwanted to show my gratitude somehow..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "I need t'properly repay you for your kind\r\nwords. So, please give me some time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "N-No, don't think about it too much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Wait, Kiryu-san!?\r\nMan, he marches t'his own drum..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "No, I just got here, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "What!? K-Kaneko-san...!\r\nWhy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "What do you mean \"why?\"\r\nYou told me to come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "The bar was quiet so I relaxed on the sofa,\r\nand I found a letter stashed on the table."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Oh no... By putting it on the table,\r\nKaneko-san found it instead of Mama..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Sorry. I never noticed the way you felt at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "No... Don't worry about it. You helped me\r\nout so I just wanted to show some thanks..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "I may not be much more than a boxer,\r\nbut I can handle your feelings, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "(What the hell is he on about...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "H-Hey, Kiryu-san!? What the heck?\r\nI was all fired up and everything..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "No, I just showed up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "What?! H-Hatakeyama-san...!\r\nWhy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Whaddaya mean, Kiryu-san?\r\nY'told me to show up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "When I got t'the bar, your letter\r\nwas the first thing I noticed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Oh no... The counter was too obvious. I made\r\nit too easy for someone else to pick up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Thanks, Kiryu-san.\r\nThat letter was real nice and heartfelt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "R-Right... Well, you've helped me a lot,\r\nso I thought I'd say thank you for it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "I still remember the first time you\r\ncame to the bar. Maybe it was destiny."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "M-Maybe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "H-Huh, Kiryu-san!?\r\nGeez, that guy never rests..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "No, I just got here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "What!? A-Akiyoshi-san...!\r\nWhy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?\r\nYou told me to come here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "I was thinkin' 'bout baseball when I\r\nsaw your letter behind the poster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Oh no... Obviously someone other than Mama\r\nwould notice it by the baseball poster..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "I can't tell ya how happy I felt!\r\nYour words really touched my heart, man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "R-Right... Well, you've been great at\r\nbaseball, so I wanted to say thanks..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Well, after that letter, Kiryu-san, I had t'come\r\nand tell ya my feelings too... And..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "H-Huh, Kiryu-san!?\r\nI wasn't done talking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "I'll write the letter again... But I\r\nneed to choose a better spot for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Someone other than Mama might find it\r\nhere. I should put it somewhere else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Did I make you wait?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "It's fine, I just walked up myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Good. Sorry to make you wait,\r\nand for dragging you all the way out here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I was shocked. I went t'put tea in\r\nthe pot but there was a letter inside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "No one but you uses that teapot,\r\nso I figured it'd be a good spot to put it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Then y'should've just put it in the\r\nmailbox. I always check that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Oh, the mailbox.\r\nI didn't think of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Y'don't think at all sometimes, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "But, I was happy t'get it.\r\nI've never gotten much gratitude for opening the bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Really. It'd be nice if the others could\r\nspare a thought for me like you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Well, it can be pretty tough to break\r\nthrough your guard, according to Hatakeyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "I ain't like that on purpose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "But I guess I hold men to a high standard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Yeah? An old flame?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "No way! Nothin' of the sort.\r\nMy father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Your father?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Yeah, he was a fisherman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "He was everyone's friend, strong, kind...\r\nHe was a mighty fine father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Was?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "He went out t'sea on a fishing boat one\r\nday n' never came back. It was ages ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "He was a bar fly himself, so I figured if I\r\nopened one, maybe he'd jus' stroll in one day..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "T'be honest, that's why I opened it.\r\nThe bar, I mean."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "I had no idea..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "My father may be gone, but I've laughed and\r\nhad fun with you and the others, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Heh, yeah? Well, thanks for keeping\r\nthe drinks flowing for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "And who knows, maybe your dad will see\r\nyour bar someday, so don't you close it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Yeah, which means I better get my sales up.\r\nY'better keep comin' around, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "Can't let my guard down for a second."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Looks like a ship's comin' in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I love the sound of those horns...\r\nMakes me feel like he's comin' home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san? Y'ever heard the phrase,\r\n\"Man makes the ship, women make the port?\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Hm? Not really..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "The men go out t'work on the waves,\r\nthe women protect what they come home to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Somethin' like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "Oh, I see. A man can only focus on his\r\nwork if he knows his home is safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Well, there's a few ways of seein' it,\r\nbut I think it's about pure trust, and that's beautiful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "Yeah. It's nice to have a home to go back\r\nto. A man with a port like that is lucky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "So the port makes him lucky, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "That reminds me, I never told y'my\r\nname, did I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I've always just called you Mama,\r\nbut I've never asked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "My name is Minato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "That so? Mama Minato. \r\nIt has a nice ring to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Really? Thanks. Do y'think\r\nI'll find a nice ship someday?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Heh, I'm sure you will.\r\nYou deserve a world-class ship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Y-You think so?\r\nBecause I think I've already found one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Hm? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "No, nothing. Let's head back to the bar.\r\nI left it open."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Yeah, everyone might be having a\r\ndrinking party without us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "They probably are!\r\nLet's get going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "You know, I just realized I've never\r\nasked how old you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Wise choice! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "Oh, they're here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Yer both so late!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Seriously, we were getting bored."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "How is it that you guys are all hanging\r\naround my bar without me here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Details, details, let's not sweat 'em, now.\r\nWhat matters is we're here now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Anyway, us guys've been talkin' a bit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, y'oughta take this seat here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you've helped us all out here.\r\nI hardly remember a time y'weren't around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Hear hear.\r\nI wouldn't mess with Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Kaneko-san... You guys..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "You're right. Let's gather 'round Kiryu-san\r\nand lift a glass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "Oh, amazing, Kiryu-san!\r\nI think that was Mama's approval!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Move yer butt, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Oh... Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "(Hmm, I didn't add to the conversation\r\nand it ended awkwardly.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "(They're still in the bar. I should\r\nclear my head and get back in there.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "(Bars... You walk in to share a drink and a laugh,\r\nbut sometimes you walk out with a story...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "(Stories that turn strangers into family.\r\nI like this little family. I'll never forget them.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Whew, I'm feeling kinda buzzed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "The more y'drink, the more fun it gets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Well guys, I'll see you around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Soon I hope?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "We'll be here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Thanks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!\r\nI've been waiting!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "I heard from my diver friends that you\r\ngo spearfishing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "In that case, I have a present I want\r\nto give you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "A present for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "Yep, here.\r\nIt's yours!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "It's... a speargun. \r\nWhere did you get this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "My dad and I used t'spearfish\r\na little ourselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "This was the gun I used. Talkin' to\r\nyou the other day reminded me of it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "I fixed it up a bit for ya.\r\nIt's not too shabby, if I do say so myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "You're sure you want to give\r\nme something this special?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "That's exactly why I'm givin' it to ya.\r\nYou've been showin' us a great time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "Everyone seems t'be smiling more.\r\nAnd this is my way of sayin' thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Heh, I see.\r\nI'm sure I'll make great use of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "You're welcome. \r\nI'm real glad we met, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

